{"tid":1634191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手推上熱門】鶳神獸召喚指南","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:38:07.000Z","uid":305360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cbb5567fc0d81aa51a8260e3b24af09321a532d","tid":1634191,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"尋日長沙灣示威者被藍絲的士佬<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撞斷雙腿</strong></span></span>，之前荃灣少年被<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>斬斷腳筋</strong></span></span>，皆造成無辜的示威者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終身殘廢</strong></span></span>，可以話係人神共憤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">司法制度傾斜暴政，執法機關雙重標準<br />\n告人者隨時轉而成為被告，控以非法集結；<br />\n殺人傷人者以愛國既名義，完全逍遙法外！</span></span><br />\n凡此種種，皆令香港人陷入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有理不能伸</span></strong></span>的境地，<br />\n再加上最近少部分和理非開始吹「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完全停止暴力</span></strong></span>」之風<br />\n各位巴打絲打，你話合理嗎？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根本不合理！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Be WATER and WISE, doesn&rsquo;t mean be WEAK and be KIND!</span></strong></span><br />\n就我觀察，部分非常不合理既神獸召喚，完全係有狗或者有鬼係度自編自導，嘗試令輿論反轉！<br />\n所以現推出「香城 Online 神獸召喚指南」，有能力既兄弟，可以幫手整下方形文宣圖，然後 post 去 IG。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【香城 Online 召喚師守則】</strong></span></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一星黃鶳</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<strong>召喚條件：影人大頭 指罵挑機 撕紙狗<br />\n召喚效果：聲波攻擊 群眾壓力</strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">二星藍鶳</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<strong>召喚條件：空手襲擊示威者<br />\n召喚效果：肢體制服 小懲大戒 不見血</strong><br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三星紅鶳</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<strong>召喚條件：持械恫嚇示威者<br />\n召喚效果：見血 但不至傷殘</strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>四星黑鶳</strong></span></ins><br />\n<strong>召喚條件：持械攻擊 或 造成示威者重傷 eg 元朗白衣人 黑社會 長沙灣的士佬 二坡坊斬人案<br />\n召喚效果： <br />\n1）必須四肢傷殘<br />\n2）召喚 一星 二星 隔絕阻膠</strong><br />\n<br />\n係而家咁既時勢&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">極權繼續欺壓，公義未能彰顯<br />\n一日狗隊未撥亂反正、未正式解散<br />\n以上既自衛，完全係合情合理！</span></strong></span><br />\n否則我地只會睇到越來越多既斬人案，以及越來越多既撞示威者案件！<br />\n<br />\n同意既，麻煩比個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有心既巴打，可以順手推一推，萬分感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2212d29645def13431cb29fcde69e70cc4503f","tid":1634191,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日全民三罷！！！</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oi5w3dZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foi5w3dZ.png&h=66325756&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e705f8e76e70b495b74f27d0c68b86f0a98f330","tid":1634191,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbb5567fc0d81aa51a8260e3b24af09321a532d","tid":1634191,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"尋日長沙灣示威者被藍絲的士佬<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撞斷雙腿</strong></span></span>，之前荃灣少年被<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>斬斷腳筋</strong></span></span>，皆造成無辜的示威者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終身